{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "190f3c43-cd3f-4080-a278-a3437f0977c6",
    "name": "XMeme API Collection",
    "description": "Complete Postman collection for testing the XMeme - Meme Sharing Backend REST API.\n\nBase URL: http://localhost:8081\n\n## Features:\n- POST a meme: creates a new entry and returns its unique ID\n- GET latest 100 memes: sorted by creation date (newest first)\n- GET a single meme by ID\n- PATCH a meme: update URL and/or caption (name is immutable)\n- DELETE a meme by ID\n\n## Testing Order:\n1. Create memes (valid and invalid scenarios)\n2. Browse all memes\n3. Get specific meme by ID\n4. Update meme details\n5. Delete memes\n6. Test error scenarios (404, 409, 400)\n\n## Tech Stack:\n- Spring Boot 2.7.1\n- MongoDB 6.0\n- Spring Data MongoDB",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "12884920"
  },
